name: A Pact with the Moon
description:
(NEVER TO BE SWAPPED)

This is a pact between Creator and Collector. Whomever's name appears on this card is recognized to hold the most editions of TradScape. This person and this person alone will have the ability to reserve an edition of any standard 5/5 TradScape objkt prior to drop. If a new collector claims the title, this objkt will be burned. Another shall take it's place.
